  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a large saucepan, bring 2 cups of water to a boil.",
    "Add 1 cup of Uruguayan rice and cook according to package directions.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together 2 large eggs and 2 tbsp of Dijon mustard.",
    "Once the rice is cooked, stir in the egg mixture and season with salt and black pepper.",
